[This outbreak has yet to be declared a confirmed anthrax outbreak. They say they should have confirmation by Thu 17 Aug 2016. In the meanwhile, the buffalo carcasses have been burnt.

For a fuller description of the wildlife losses due to the current flooding, here are two reports:
http://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/rhinos-in-kaziranga-caught-between-floods-and-poachers-bullets/story-lB6ACek82KZ3fsRy7L58MN.html,
